{
  "texts": [
    "Crypto is still subject to many risks for investors and users.",
    "One of the main risks for investors is that the value is highly volatile and fluctuates significantly in short periods.",
    "This makes crypto price and value extremely difficult to predict, leading to significant losses when the value drops significantly.",
    "Since crypto is also a speculative asset, investors cannot be confident that the value of their investment will ever recover or go to zero.",
    "Another risk is that no one, a government, or any financial institution regulate crypto."
  ]
}